title: From the Vault: Brain Soup and Liquid Brains
itunes:title: From the Vault: Brain Soup and Liquid Brains
description:
Is there ever a good scientific reason to turn brains into soup? What does all of this have to do with the concept of “liquid brains?” Robert and Joe explore on Stuff to Blow Your Mind. (Originally published 6/11/2019)
